comments: Adebayo (MIA) engages and disengages with Morris Sr. (LAC) as the pick expires.
Morris Sr. (LAC) is already in Adebayo's (MIA) path and does not deliver illegal contact as the defensive switch occurs simultaneously to the pick being set.
Butler (MIA) brings his right arm forward and marginal contact occurs with George's (LAC) front as George dribbles toward the middle of the floor.
Adebayo (MIA) firms up over his right foot and absorbs the contact that occurs with Batum (LAC) as the pick is set.
Batum (LAC) legally contests Herro's (MIA) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Adebayo (MIA) brings his left hand forward as he pursues the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Zubac's (LAC) right arm prior to Zubac gaining control of the ball.
Adebayo (MIA) engages and disengages with Zubac (LAC) as Zubac moves to set the pick.
Martin (MIA) and Zubac (LAC) engage and disengage with one another as they move toward the lane following the expiration of the pick.
Adebayo (MIA) brings his hands forward toward George's (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs with George's front as George drives toward the lane.
Adebayo (MIA) moves alongside George's (LAC) path and legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Batum (LAC) brings his right hand forward and marginal contact occurs with Herro's (MIA) left side after Herro has already lost control of the ball during the inbound.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Herro (MIA) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Martin (MIA) engages and disengages with Morris Sr. (LAC) after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Jackson (LAC) is already in Strus' (MIA) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs as they come together off-ball.
Jackson (LAC) maintains a bent hand on Butler's (MIA) side and marginal contact occurs as Butler backs Jackson down in the post.
Butler (MIA) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two steps before starting his upward shooting motion.
Jackson (LAC) contests the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Butler's (MIA) arm after the release.
Martin (MIA) brushes George's (LAC) right leg and marginal contact occurs in the post.
Zubac (LAC) and Adebayo (MIA) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
George (LAC) turns as he moves laterally and initiates body contact with Butler (MIA) along the sideline, affecting Butler's SQBR.
Zubac (LAC) and Adebayo (MIA) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.

A jump ball is initially called to determine possession. Replay review of the out of bounds call pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. George's (LAC) leg touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds and Miami was awarded possession. The game clock was reset to 42.1 seconds.
George (LAC) moves forward slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Adebayo's (MIA) side/back. George then makes clean contact with the ball as Adebayo makes the pass.
Butler (MIA) and Jackson (LAC) make incidental leg-to-leg contact after the pass attempt is deflected.
Martin (MIA) does not inbound the ball within five seconds.
Jackson (LAC) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Zubac (LAC) and Adebayo (MIA) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Batum (LAC) and Zubac (LAC) move forward slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Adebayo's (MIA) back and side as they double team Adebayo near mid-court.

Adebayo's (MIA) right foot lands in the backcourt prior to when he releases the ball. The Miami bench signals for a timeout after Adebayo's foot has already landed and therefore the timeout was not recognized.
Martin (MIA) and George (LAC) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Herro (MIA) brings his left forearm toward Jackson's (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs with Jackson's front as he drives toward the lane.
Jackson (LAC) brings his off-arm outward and marginal contact occurs with Herro's (MIA) left arm as he defends the drive.
George (LAC) is moving away from Martin (MIA) prior to marginal body contact occurring as Martin moves to defend the shot attempt.
Martin (MIA) and Herro (MIA) legally contest Jackson's (LAC) driving shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from George (LAC) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Jackson (LAC) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Strus (MIA) legally contests Jackson's (LAC) driving shot attempt.
Batum (LAC) brushes Herro's (MIA) right side and marginal contact occurs as Herro makes the pass.
